Place cubed potatoes in large microwaveable bowl; microwave on HIGH 5 min., stirring after 2-1/2 min. Add broth and milk to bowl; stir. Microwave on HIGH 10 min., stirring after 5 min. Crush potatoes with a potato masher. Reserve 2 Tbsp. each of the bacon and cheese and 1 Tbsp. of the onions for topping; set aside. Add remaining bacon, cheese and onions to soup. Serve topped with reserved bacon, cheese, onions and sour cream.